Package: Rtinycc
Title: Builds 'TinyCC' 'Cli' and Library for 'C' Scripting in 'R'
Version: 0.0.3.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure", 
    email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person( given ="Fabrice Bellard and tinycc Authors" , role = c("ctb"),
    comment = "Tinycc Compiler (tinycc) authors and COPYRIGHT holders")
    )
Description: Builds 'TinyCC' (Tiny 'C' Compiler) 'cli' and library for R package use.
    This package compiles 'TinyCC' from source code and provides R functions to interact with the TinyCC compiler.
    'TinyCC' is a small and fast 'C' compiler that can be used for various purposes, including preprocessing of headers, just-in-time compilation 'C' code in 'R' for
    'C' "scripting".
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
Imports:
    lambda.r
Suggests:
    tinytest,
    treesitter.c (>= 0.0.4),
    quickr
SystemRequirements: GNU make
OS_type: unix
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
